    "The time complexity of the proposed model is calculated as; O n 2 * d, where n represents the sequence length, and d reflects the dimen- sions of the hidden state.",
    "In this study, the classification tasks are measured using the accuracy metric.",
    "It calculates the percentage of properly identified examples in a dataset relative to all occurrences.",
    "In this particular case, the number of events for a particular user is expressed by the number of folds (k = 130).",
    "The remaining instances (k-1) serve as a training set for each iteration of the learning process, and the instance that is chosen serves as a test set."
